i < groups.getLength(); i++) {\r\n            JsonObject joRoot = new JsonObject();\r\n            if (!(groups.item(i) instanceof Element))\r\n                continue;\r\n            joRoot.put(\"root_tag_name\", groups.item(i).getNodeName());\r\n            NamedNodeMap attrs = groups.item(i).getAttributes();\r\n            for (int j = 0; j < attrs.getLength(); ++j) {\r\n                Node attr = attrs.item(j);\r\n                joRoot.put(attr.getNodeName(), attr.getNodeValue());\r\n            }\r\n            Node group = groups.item(i);\r\n            if (group instanceof Element) {\r\n                Element groupElement = (Element) group;\r\n                NodeList patterns = groupElement.getElementsByTagName(\"Pattern\");\r\n                for (int j = 0; j < patterns.getLength(); j++) {\r\n                    JsonObject joPattern = new JsonObject();\r\n                    Node patElement = patterns.item(j);\r\n                    joPattern.put(\"pattern_tag_name\", patElement.getNodeName());\r\n                    NamedNodeMap atts = patElement.getAttributes();\r\n                    for (int k = 0; k < atts.getLength(); k++) {\r\n                        Node att = atts.item(k);\r\n                        joPattern.put(att.getNodeName(), att.getNodeValue());\r\n                    }\r\n                    joPattern.put(\"text\", patElement.getTextContent());\r\n                    joPattern.mergeIn(joRoot.copy());\r\n                    eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), joPattern, addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg));\r\n                    resultOutboundCount++;\r\n                    //System.out.println(\"Pattern#\" + i + \": \" + joPattern.toString());\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        //System.out.println(\"joRoot: \" + joRoot.toString());\r\n\r\n        resultOutboundCount++;\r\n        eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), \"finished\");\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    private void sendError(Message msg, Exception e) {\r\n        eb.publish(addressBook.getError(), msg.body(), addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg).addHeader(\"error\", e.getMessage()));\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    private Document convertStringToXMLDocument(String xmlString) {\r\n\r\n        try {\r\n            //Parse the content to Document object\r\n            Document doc = builder.parse(new InputSource(new StringReader(xmlString)));\r\n            return doc;\r\n        } catch (Exception e) {\r\n            e.printStackTrace();\r\n        }\r\n        return null;\r\n    }\r\n}",

       \"<h2 style=\\\"display: inline-block; margin: 0;color: %s\\\">%s</h2>\";\r\n    private static ArrayList<String> stmtList = new ArrayList<>();\r\n\r\n    @Override\r\n    public void }\r\n\r\n    private void sendLabels() {\r\n        sendLabel(String.format(label, stmtCount == 0 ? \"red\" : \"#0043ff\", stmtCount), \"18ff96\", \"50\", \"efff18\");\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    @Override\r\n    public <T> void noCmd(Message<T> tMessage, String cmd) {\r\n        stmtCount = 0;\r\n        stmtList.clear();\r\n        String SQL = \"SELECT * FROM tblStmt\";\r\n        String stmtDesc);\r\n                stmtList.add(stmtCode);\r\n                stmtCount++;\r\n            }\r\n            sendLabels();\r\n            con.close();\r\n            Set keySet = this.stmts.keySet();\r\n            keySet.forEach(key -> {\r\n                if (!stmtList.contains(key))\r\n                    stmts.remove(key);\r\n            });\r\n            watch.stop();\r\n            long millis = watch.getTime();\r\n            long minutes = (millis / 1000) / 60;\r\n            int seconds = (int) ((millis / 1000) % 60);\r\n            System.out.println(\"Stmt loaded. count: \" + stmtCount + \" time elapsed: \" + minutes + \":\" + seconds);\r\n            eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), new JsonObject().put(\"msg\", branchesCount = 0;\r\n        branchesList.clear();\r\n        String SQL = \"SELECT * FROM tblBranches\";\r\n        String connectionUrl = \"jdbc:sqlserver://\" + obrs_db.getString(\"ip\") + \":\" + obrs_db.getInteger(\"port\") +\r\n                \";responseBuffering=adaptive;DatabaseName=\" + obrs_db.getString(\"dbName\") + \";user=\" +\r\n                obrs_db.getString(\"user\") + \";password=\" + obrs_db.getString(\"pass\");\r\n        try (Connection con = DriverManager.getConnection(connectionUrl);\r\n             Statement stmt = con.createStatement();) {\r\n            StopWatch watch = new StopWatch();\r\n            System.out.println(\"Loading branches table started!\");\r\n            watch.start();\r\n            ResultSet rs = stmt.executeQuery(SQL);\r\n            StringBuilder remainder = new StringBuilder();\r\n            while (rs.next()) {\r\n                String branchCode = rs.getString(\"BranchCode\").trim();\r\n                String branchName = rs.getString(\"BranchName\").trim();\r\n                branches.put(branchCode, branchName);\r\n                branchesList.add(branchCode);\r\n                branchesCount++;\r\n            }\r\n            sendLabels();\r\n            con.close();\r\n            Set keySet = this.branches.keySet();\r\n            keySet.forEach(key -> {\r\n                if (!branchesList.contains(key))\r\n                    branches.remove(key);\r\n            });\r\n            watch.stop();\r\n            long millis = watch.getTime();\r\n            long minutes = (millis / 1000) / 60;\r\n            int seconds = (int) ((millis / 1000) % 60);\r\n            System.out.println(\"Branches loaded. count: \" + branchesCount + \" time elapsed: \" + minutes + \":\" + seconds);\r\n            eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), new JsonObject().put(\"msg\", \"result-set-end\"),\r\n                    addressBook.getDeliveryOptions().addHeader(\"cmd\", \"status\").addHeader(\"name\", \"branches\"));\r\n            resultOutboundCount++;\r\n        } catch (SQLException e) {\r\n            e.printStackTrace();\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}",

     if (aKey.isEmpty())  // used for forced \"SendSMS\" messages without key\r\n                return true;\r\n            String aKeyId = aKey.substring(0, keyLen);\r\n            if TreeSet<String> all = new TreeSet<String>();\r\n        StringBuilder masksStr = new StringBuilder(masks);\r\n        while (masksStr.length() > 0) {\r\n            String mask =          for (String file : files) {\r\n                if (file.contains(\".$\"))\r\n                    continue;\r\n                all.add(file);\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        return all.toArray(new String[all.size()]);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    public void clearFiles() {\r\n        final long MILLIS_IN_A_DAY = 1000 * 60 * 60 * 24;\r\n        long dt = new Date().getTime() - }\r\n    }\r\n}",

body.getJsonObject(\"smsInfo\") : body.getJsonObject(\"tran\");\r\n        JsonArray phoneNos = new JsonArray(List.of(smsInfo.getString(\"phoneNos\")));\r\n        phoneNos.forEach(phoneNo -> {\r\n            for (int i = 0; i < filters.size(); i++) {\r\n                if (filters.get(i).allow((String) phoneNo)) {\r\n                    publishOut(i, body.copy(), addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg)\r\n                            .addHeader(\"phoneNo\", (String) phoneNo)\r\n                            .addHeader(\"sendRefNo2\", ++curSendRefNo2 + \"\")\r\n                            .addHeader(\"providerName\", providers.getJsonObject(i).getString(\"providerName\"))\r\n                            .addHeader(\"srcPhoneNo\", providers.getJsonObject(i).getInteger(\"srcPhoneNo\") + \"\"));\r\n                    break;//If there is more provider to send then \"comment out\" the break!\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    @Override\r\n    public <T> void status(Message<T> msg) {\r\n        if (msg.headers().contains(\"name\") && msg.headers().get(\"name\").equals(\"MaxSendRefNo2\")) {\r\n            this.curSendRefNo2 = Long.parseLong(((JsonObject) msg.body()).getString(\"MaxSendRefNo2\"));\r\n            System.out.println(\"curSendRefNo2 = \" + curSendRefNo2);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}",

lineSplit[13] : lineSplit[1].substring(0, 6));\r\n                suny.put(\"TxnTime\", lineSplit[14].trim().length() == 6 ? lineSplit[14] : lineSplit[1].substring(6, 12));\r\n                suny.put(\"TerminalID\", lineSplit[15]);\r\n                suny.put(\"SeqNo\", lineSplit[16]);\r\n                suny.put(\"VariableData\", lineSplit[17]);\r\n                suny.put(\"OptionalInfo\", lineSplit[18]);\r\n                suny.put(\"Comment3\", lineSplit[19]);\r\n                suny.put(\"Balance\", lineSplit[20]);\r\n                suny.put(\"EqualRialAmount\", lineSplit[21]);\r\n                suny.put(\"CARD_PAN1\", lineSplit[22]);\r\n                suny.put(\"CARD_PAN2\", lineSplit[23]);\r\n                suny.put(\"CARD_ACNO1\", lineSplit[24]);\r\n                suny.put(\"CARD_ACNO2\", lineSplit[25]);\r\n                suny.put(\"PRCODE\", lineSplit[26]);\r\n                suny.put(\"ACQ_BIN\", lineSplit[27]);\r\n                suny.put(\"ISS_BIN \", lineSplit[28]);\r\n                suny.put(\"OPERCODE\", lineSplit[29]);\r\n                suny.put(\"rawSuny\", rawSuny);\r\n                eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), new JsonObject().put(\"tran\", suny)\r\n                        .put(\"rawData\", rawSuny).put(\"channel\", \"MQ|Suny\").put(\"tranType\", \"MQSuny\"));\r\n                resultOutboundCount++;\r\n            }\r\n        } else {\r\n            sendError(msg);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    private <T> void sendError(Message<T> msg){\r\n        eb.publish(addressBook.getError(), msg.body(), addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg)\r\n                .addHeader(\"status\", \"error\")\r\n                .addHeader(\"error\", \"Suny format is not compatible.\"));\r\n        errorOutboundCount++;\r\n    }\r\n}",

i < groups.getLength(); i++) {\r\n            JsonObject joRoot = new JsonObject();\r\n            if (!(groups.item(i) instanceof Element))\r\n                continue;\r\n            joRoot.put(\"root_tag_name\", groups.item(i).getNodeName());\r\n            NamedNodeMap attrs = groups.item(i).getAttributes();\r\n            for (int j = 0; j < attrs.getLength(); ++j) {\r\n                Node attr = attrs.item(j);\r\n                joRoot.put(attr.getNodeName(), attr.getNodeValue());\r\n            }\r\n            Node group = groups.item(i);\r\n            if (group instanceof Element) {\r\n                Element groupElement = (Element) group;\r\n                NodeList patterns = groupElement.getElementsByTagName(\"Query\");\r\n                for (int j = 0; j < patterns.getLength(); j++) {\r\n                    JsonObject joPattern = new JsonObject();\r\n                    Node patElement = patterns.item(j);\r\n                    joPattern.put(\"sql_tag_name\", patElement.getNodeName());\r\n                    NamedNodeMap atts = patElement.getAttributes();\r\n                    for (int k = 0; k < atts.getLength(); k++) {\r\n                        Node att = atts.item(k);\r\n                        joPattern.put(att.getNodeName(), att.getNodeValue());\r\n                    }\r\n                    joPattern.put(\"text\", patElement.getTextContent());\r\n                    joPattern.mergeIn(joRoot.copy());\r\n                    eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), joPattern, addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg));\r\n                    resultOutboundCount++;\r\n                    //System.out.println(\"Pattern#\" + i + \": \" + joPattern.toString());\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        //System.out.println(\"joRoot: \" + joRoot.toString());\r\n\r\n        resultOutboundCount++;\r\n        eb.publish(addressBook.getResult(), \"finished\");\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    private void sendError(Message msg, Exception e) {\r\n        eb.publish(addressBook.getError(), msg.body(), addressBook.getDeliveryOptions(msg).addHeader(\"error\", e.getMessage()));\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    private Document convertStringToXMLDocument(String xmlString) {\r\n\r\n        try {\r\n            //Parse the content to Document object\r\n            Document doc = builder.parse(new InputSource(new StringReader(xmlString)));\r\n            return doc;\r\n        } catch (Exception e) {\r\n            e.printStackTrace();\r\n        }\r\n        return null;\r\n    }\r\n}",
